<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>888 - 문자발송</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/main.css?v=20260226_225841" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/send_2x2.css?v=20260227_094116" />
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="container header-inner">
    <a class="brand" href="/">888</a>

    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/send.html">문자발송</a>
      <a href="/addr.html">주소록</a>
      <a href="/result.html">전송결과</a>
      <a href="/charge.html">충전하기</a>

      <!-- ===== 기업용 확장 메뉴 (비활성) ===== -->
      <!-- <a href="/statistics.html">통계</a> -->
      <!-- <a href="/api.html">API연동</a> -->
      <!-- <a href="/admin.html">관리자</a> -->
      <!-- <a href="/audit.html">감사로그</a> -->
    </nav>

    <div class="header-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/login.html">로그인</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="site-main">
  

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid2">

        <!-- LEFT -->
        <div class="panel" style="padding:26px">

          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:flex-end">
            <div style="font-weight:950">수신번호 입력</div>
            <div style="opacity:.6;font-size:13px">
              붙여넣기 최대 <b id="maxPaste">-</b>건 · 엑셀 최대 <b id="maxExcel">-</b>건
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tabs" style="margin-top:12px">
            <button class="tab on" data-tab="manual">직접작성</button>
            <button class="tab" data-tab="paste">붙여넣기</button>
            <button class="tab" data-tab="excel">엑셀 업로드</button>
          </div>

          <div class="tabpane on" id="tab-manual" style="margin-top:12px">
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 140px;gap:10px;align-items:end">
              <div>
                <div class="lbl">번호 입력</div>
                <input id="manualInput" class="inp" type="text" placeholder="예) 01012345678" />
              </div>
              <button id="manualAdd" class="btn" type="button">추가</button>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:10px;opacity:.65;font-size:13px">* 번호만 입력하면 자동 정리(하이픈 제거)됩니다.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="tabpane" id="tab-paste" style="margin-top:12px">
            <div class="lbl">여러 건 붙여넣기</div>
            <textarea id="pasteArea" class="txt" style="min-height:130px" placeholder="01011112222&#10;01033334444&#10;(줄바꿈/쉼표/공백 가능)"></textarea>
            <div style="margin-top:10px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
              <div style="opacity:.65;font-size:13px">현재 추출 <b id="pasteCount">0</b>건</div>
              <button id="pasteApply" class="btn" type="button">적용</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tabpane" id="tab-excel" style="margin-top:12px">
            <div class="lbl">엑셀 업로드 (.xlsx)</div>
            <input id="excelFile" class="inp" type="file" accept=".xlsx" />
            <div style="margin-top:10px;opacity:.65;font-size:13px">* 1열(A)에 전화번호만 있다고 가정(나중에 규칙 확장 가능)</div>
            <div style="margin-top:12px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
              <div style="opacity:.65;font-size:13px">현재 추출 <b id="excelCount">0</b>건</div>
              <button id="excelApply" class="btn" type="button" disabled style="opacity:.55;cursor:not-allowed">적용(준비중)</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-top:18px">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:flex-end">
              <div style="font-weight:950">수신자 목록</div>
              <div style="opacity:.65;font-size:13px">총 <b id="toCount">0</b>건</div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel" style="margin-top:10px;padding:14px;border-radius:18px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)">
              <div id="toList" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px"></div>
              <div id="toEmpty" style="opacity:.55">수신번호를 추가하세요.</div>
              <div style="margin-top:12px;display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
                <a class="btn" href="/addr.html">주소록에서 선택</a>
                <button id="clearTo" class="btn" type="button">전체삭제</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-top:18px">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:flex-end">
              <div style="font-weight:950">메시지</div>
              <div style="opacity:.65;font-size:13px">
                바이트 <b id="byteNow">0</b> / <b id="byteLimit">문서확정필요</b> (초과 시 분할발송)
              </div>
            </div>

            <textarea id="msg" class="txt" style="min-height:180px;margin-top:10px" placeholder="메시지 내용을 입력"></textarea>

            <div style="margin-top:12px;display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between">
              <div style="opacity:.6;font-size:13px">보안 정책: 메시지 원문 저장 없음(연동앱에서 처리)</div>
              <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
                <button id="btnTest" class="btn" type="button">테스트 발송</button>
                <button id="btnSend" class="btn btn-primary" type="button">문자 발송</button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel" style="margin-top:14px;padding:14px;border-radius:18px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)">
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
                <div style="font-weight:950">테스트 상태</div>
                <div id="testTimer" style="opacity:.7">대기</div>
              </div>
              <div style="margin-top:10px;display:grid;gap:8px">
                <div class="rowline"><span class="badge">T1</span> <span id="t1">-</span></div>
                <div class="rowline"><span class="badge">T2</span> <span id="t2">-</span></div>
                <div class="rowline"><span class="badge">T3</span> <span id="t3">-</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel" style="margin-top:14px;padding:14px;border-radius:18px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)">
              <div style="font-weight:950;margin-bottom:10px">최근 테스트 (최대 3개)</div>
              <div id="testHistory" style="display:grid;gap:10px;opacity:.85"></div>
              <div id="testHistoryEmpty" style="opacity:.55">기록 없음</div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT -->
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:22px">
          <div class="panel grid" style="padding:22px">
            <div style="font-weight:950;margin-bottom:12px">Preview</div>
            <div class="phone">
              <div class="phone-top"><div class="phone-notch"></div></div>
              <div class="phone-screen">
                <div class="phone-title">Message</div>
                <div class="bubble" id="previewBubble">내용을 입력하면 미리보기가 표시됩니다.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="phone-bottom"></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:12px;opacity:.65;font-size:13px">* 실제 폰 화면과 100% 동일하진 않지만 “보이는 느낌”은 맞춤</div>
          </div>

          <div class="panel" style="padding:22px">
            <div style="font-weight:950;margin-bottom:10px">Rules</div>
            <div style="opacity:.7;line-height:1.75">
              • 번호 입력: 직접/붙여넣기/엑셀 업로드<br/>
              • 붙여넣기/엑셀 최대 건수 초과 시 차단<br/>
              • 바이트 초과 시 분할발송(연동앱 정책)<br/>
              • 테스트는 40초 제한(미응답=실패)<br/>
              • 최근 테스트 3건만 저장
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="panel" style="padding:22px">
            <div style="font-weight:950;margin-bottom:10px">Secure Contact</div>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://t.me/Dr_simpson_99" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="width:100%">텔레그램 상담 연결</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
<section><div class="container"><div class="panel" style="padding:18px;display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap">
<button id="btnTest" class="btn" type="button" onclick="alert("CLICK OK: TEST")">테스트 발송</button>
<button id="btnSend" class="btn btn-primary" type="button" onclick="alert("CLICK OK: SEND")">문자 발송</button>
</div></div></section>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="container footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-left">
      <div class="footer-brand">888</div>
      <div class="footer-meta"><span>© 888 All rights reserved.</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-right">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://t.me/Dr_simpson_99" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">텔레그램 상담</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="/assets/js/sections.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/xlsx@0.18.5/dist/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<script src="/assets/js/send.js"></script>
<script src="/assets/js/clickprobe.js"></script>
<script src="/assets/js/send_patch.js"></script>
<script src="/assets/js/send_2x2.js?v=20260227_094116"></script>
</body>
</html>
